path.desc: This is a teleport link between Neboo and Alderaan.
path.title: Neboo Alderaan Link

path.desc:
The Western line connects Epsilon to Falconhurst RAA, extending west, south and west.
On it lie, going outward:
Epsilon, Eta, Tentholm, Whitewall, Swhump, Falconhurst, Falconhurst RAA
It connects to the Circle Line at Epsilon, and Honkwig Line at Eta.
path.title: Western Line

path.desc:
This line connects Iota to Laputa, and serves as a transfer between Skyrail and Searail.
It connects to the Northern Line at Iota, and to the Searail at Laputa.
path.title: Iota Transfer

path.desc:
This is the entire Searail network.
It connects to the Iota Transfer at Laputa.
path.title: Sea Rail

path.desc: This is a teleport link between Syco RAA and Poniri RAA.
path.title: Syco Poniri Link

path.desc:
This is the entire Nether Rail network.
Due to the low number of junctions, it is currently not split into lines.
path.title: Nether Rail

path.desc:
This line connects Gull Island, Poniri and Poniri RAA.
It does not connect to the rest of the Skyrail network, but is reachable by teleport via Poniri RAA.
path.title: Poniri Line

path.desc:
This line connects Eta to Honkwig.
It connects to the Western Line at Eta.
path.title: Honkwig Line

path.desc:
This line connects Zeta to the Deacon Outpost.
It connects to the Northern Line at Zeta.
path.title: Deacon Line

path.desc:
This line connects Syco HQ to North Vandia, extending north.
On it lie, going outward: Syco HQ, Syco Junction, Welcome Center, Iota, Zeta, North Vandia.
It connects to the Circle Line at Syco HQ, the Stadium Line at Syco Junction, the Sea/Sky Transfer at Iota and the Deacon Line at Zeta.
path.title: Northern Line

path.desc:
This line connects Delta to Dagobah Temple.
It connects to the Circle Line at Delta.
path.title: Dagobah Line
Meridian Line
path.desc:
This line connects Alpha and Beta, extending southward. It lies precisely on x=0, and is dubbed the Meridian Line.
On it lie, from north to south:
- Beta - The Spire - Outer Haven - Neboo - Iffy - Alpha - Dikiyobia - Fort Rockfall - Dashite Bluff
It connects to the Circle Line at Alpha and Beta.

This line connects Gamma to the Hyphean Outpost.
It connects to the Circle Line at Gamma.
path.title: Hyphean Line
Circle Line
path.desc:
This segment of Skyrail connects the junctions Alpha, Beta, Gamma, Delta and Epsilon in a grand rectangle spanned between Gamma and Epsilon, and is dubbed the Circle Line.
On this line lie, in clockwise order from Alpha: - Alpha, Alpha RAA, Epsilon, Massive Shaft, Trenton, Entertainment Center, Beta, Syco HQ, Syco RAA, Gamma, Delta, Proving Grounds, Drypeak.
It connects to the Western Line at Epsilon, the Meridian Line at Alpha and Beta, the Northern Line at Syco HQ, the Hyphean Line at Gamma, and the Dagobah Line at Delta.
This is a teleport link between Alpha RAA and Falconhurst RAA.
path.title: Alpha Falconhurst Link
